# New IC for LiDaR

> the new high-speed comparator and high-bandwidth transimpedance amplifiers enable 10mph (15km/h) faster autonomous driving at highway speeds 
> by providing more than 2x higher bandwidth and accommodating 32 additional channels (128 vs. 96) to a LiDAR module within the same module size.
> [source MXM](https://www.maximintegrated.com/en/aboutus/newsroom/2020/industry-s-smallest-lidar-ics-by-maxim-offer-more-than-2x-higher-bandwidth-for-faster-self-driving-cars.html)
